dct_title_s: Newark Colleges of Rutgers University, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map of the Newark Colleges of Rutgers University, the State University of New Jersey, including inset of northern-most buildings of the campus. Buildings are numbered for directory which shows lists the street address for each along with the specific schools continued at each address. Significant non-university landmarks (railroad stations, parks, museums) are also specified individually.
